Izetbegovic, presidents of Croatia and Bosnia, are to hold talks 
with the Yugoslavia mediators at the Petersberg [government 
guest house] near Bonn. Kinkel will then meet Tudjman and 
Izetbegovic on Saturday afternoon. 

