warring factions in Bosnia must realize that the UN 
peacekeepers' patience there is at an end. He said that if the 
factions are not interested in making peace, Canada will pull 
its peacekeepers out of Bosnia and send them home. Mr. Ouellet 
spoke to reporters in Brussels in advance of tomorrow's NATO 
