<H3> <TI>   Government To Withdraw UN Somalia Contingent in March </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD0701194994 Stockholm Radio Sweden in English 1715 GMT 7 
Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0701194994 </F>
<F P=104>  Stockholm Radio Sweden </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] The Norwegian defense minister says his nation will 
pull its 130-man UN force out of Somalia by the end of March. 
He adds that Norway is also considering removing its 280 
soldiers from the Nordic [word indistinct] in Bosnia, if the 
major supporters of the UN peacekeeping operation there decide 
to leave the area. 

</TEXT>

