Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] A strong earthquake measuring 5.7 degrees on the 
Richter scale occurred at 0923 [0723 GMT] today, 305 km 
southwest of Athens. Its epicenter was in the sea south of 
Messinia and west of Crete. 

